description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Beach Umbrella
-Sunflower Field
-Shirakawa-go in Summer
-Okinawan sea and  guardian lions statue
-Banana Flower
-Surf Boards
-Milky Way
-Rainbow in the blue sky
-Summer Sky in Shonan
-Fireworks
name: Summer Colors
